www-subtext: Wana mukana wemhinduro dzakavhurika dzinosvika miriyoni imwe nemazana maviri kuburikidza neiyi dashibhodhi inodyidzana, chishandiso chakasiyana chinobatanidza manzwi evakadzi nevasikana nemikana isingaperi yekuongorora dhijitari.
midwives-voices-subtext: Takabvunza vananyamukuta pasi rose mubvunzo: “Chii chaunonyanyoda mubasa rako sanyamukuta?”
pmnch-subtext: Kugamuchirwa ku "Zvinodiwa Nevechiduku" Dashboard! Ichi chishandiso chinopindirana chinopa mufananidzo unooneka wemhinduro uye maonero atiri kuunganidza kubva kune vechidiki vane makore 10-24 pasi rose. Nheyo yeiyi yekutanga mubvunzo wakazaruka: "Kuvandudza hupenyu hwangu, ndinoda ...". Vechidiki kubva pasi rose vanga vachipindura izvi, vachitipa maonero akasiyana mune zvavanoda, tariro, uye zvavanoshuvira. Ongorora iyo data, tsvaga nyaya dziri kumashure kwenhamba, uye ubatane nesu mukukudza manzwi evadiki bhiriyoni 1.8 pasi rese. Kuti udzidze zvakawanda nezvemushandirapamwe, shanya http://www.1point8.org.
to-protect-anonymity: Kudzivirira kusazivikanwa, vamwe vakapindura vakabviswa kubva pane iyi dashboard.
